cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.PF. 

The paper deals with a queueing system with scheduling, routing, and service time distribution control, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The system is also a control system (cs.SY) and involves heavy-tailed distributions (cs.DS) and performance analysis (cs.PF).
